snippet: The Best of Show for this year’s Concorso Italiano went to a 1969 Lamborghini Miura.
abstract: The Best of Show for this year’s Concorso Italiano went to a 1969 Lamborghini Miura.
lead_paragraph: The winner at this year’s Concorso Italiano, in Monterey, Calif., is a lime green 1969 Lamborghini Miura P400S, owned by Mark Jansen of Brisbane, Australia.

headline.main: Pebble Beach Weekend: Concorso Italiano Best of Show Announced
